cs.MA, cs.SI, cs.CE, cs.SY, cs.AI 

The paper discusses multi-level agent-based modeling, which is a subfield of multi-agent systems (MAS) and simulation. Therefore, cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses social, flow, biological, and biomedical models, which are related to complex systems, computational biology, and artificial intelligence. Hence, cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely categories.
